{"tid":26823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊做野趕絕唔守規矩煙剷","createTime":"2016-12-07T03:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T10:41:31.000Z","uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74c09cebf3d93cc305e7d2811f98c215a449e7a1","tid":26823,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咁的 <br />\n話說我有時會去機舖打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但次次都有HIHI起機舖食煙整到我成身煙味fuck <br />\n<br />\n所以我今日去機舖打機前先打去控煙辦投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩點打去投訴, 五點就有一隊八個控煙督察去機舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一連捉左五件食煙既MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有件MK寸柒柒唔肯比身份証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地CALL警察來 <br />\nMK最後就範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家都可以做下好市民 <br />\n玩死唔守規矩食煙既HIHI <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD食煙HIHI咁撚多錢食煙 <br />\n都唔志在比人罰一千幾佰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n控煙辦電話: <br />\n29618823<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e0db8cf9c4a61759801e8eb4234a7cace18559e2","tid":26823,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:07:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投訴信template<br />\n<br />\ntobaccocontrol@dh.gov.hk <br />\n<br />\n控煙辦執事先生: <br />\n<br />\n本人投訴 <br />\nXXX遊戲機中心 <br />\n地址: XXXXX <br />\n時間: XXXXX 有多人違反《 吸 煙 ( 公 眾 衛 生 ) 條 例 》 ( 香 港 法 例 第 371 章 ) <br />\n請貴辦公室更進以上投訴並以電郵回覆跟進情況 <br />\n<br />\n謝謝! <br />\n<br />\n投訴人 <br />\nXXX</blockquote>"},{"pid":"06473d32b36673e16f6a8e5cfe982176eb172d78","tid":26823,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說之前我好唔妥某機舖好撚多人食煙煙撚到尊貴既我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就打去控煙辦電話 : 29618823 <br />\n投訴!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講低左比個接線生知... <br />\n<br />\n1. 機舖地址, 名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 邊個時間最多人食煙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 我既聯絡電話, 姓氏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔想留電話既, 佢會講低檔案編號比你知, 你之後可以再打返去問佢更進情況)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後, 食花生....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日收到個回覆如下: <br />\n<br />\n屈先生: <br />\n<br />\n多謝你於7月8日玫電控煙辦公室報告XXX道XXX號XXX遊戲機中心有人吸煙事宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n按照你提供的資料, 控煙督察於7月9日到達上述場匠進行巡查, 期間共發現 3 名違例吸煙者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n己即場作出票控, 控煙督察亦己教育場所負責人有關吸煙 &amp;lt;公眾衛生&amp;gt;條例的規定, 明確要求場所負責人 <br />\n<br />\n需要遵守有關規定, 而負責人亦表示明白, 本辦公室日後亦會作不定時巡查及加強執法, 巡查期間如發 <br />\n<br />\n現違例人士會即時票控而不予警告. 在此多謝你對控煙的意見, 控煙辦會繼續玫力推廣無煙文化, 以保障 <br />\n<br />\n大眾市民的健康. 如有任何查詣, 歡迎電2961 8823或1823與本辦公室聯絡. <br />\n<br />\n1823客戶服務主管 <br />\n<br />\nXXX 謹覆 <br />\n<br />\n檔案編號: X-XXXXXX <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個電話KO 3 件煙剷, 幫政府增加4500收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"79a35997a2bba1c66044b3632830b509c097fbd0","tid":26823,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買來派比D煙剷食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見佢地咁慘, 加個十幾蚊一包, 就好似殺左佢地老母咁, <br />\n鬼殺咁嘈...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我心諗, 唔撚係化, 班煙剷一定好撚窮, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚大個人, 無錢就唔撚好學人食煙啦, <br />\n仲要起度鬧政府, 屌你老母你無錢食鮑魚咁D鮑魚使唔使減價呀 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就做下好心, 買左兩包煙派比街邊D煙剷, <br />\nD 煙剷個撚個都狗衝埋來拎免費煙... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇見佢地個樣就好笑, 成個乞兒咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就用左一百蚊都唔使, 就見到成班煙剷好似乞兒咁寒寒酸酸問我拎煙食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地拎到支煙之後好撚開心, <br />\n即刻堆埋垃圾筒傍邊開餐... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乞兒真係乞兒, 有野食都要起垃圾筒傍邊食.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我下次買多幾包煙派比煙剷, 再享受做善長既樂趣先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e88035bd318d6014e1b6e3c1eae94160271bada","tid":26823,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7dcfc29229071f835a563c75ab91ff6201e90313","tid":26823,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:19:29.000Z","msg":"去波樓成日打"},{"pid":"23ab04f58c920272ec3c8bd9155478e97eed48ee","tid":26823,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e86c0c1caa53659c37a488f09d61f52c4225f7a","tid":26823,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}